The paper presents a framework for question answering that utilizes reinforcement learning and a hierarchical approach to efficiently scale to longer documents. This suggests that the paper could fall under the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper deals with information retrieval and document analysis, which could place it under the categories of information retrieval (cs.IR) and neural networks (cs.NE).
